public class SingleTargetNotificationResponse
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates the response of a single target to a NotificationRequest. If the message could be delivered, which can be checked by inspecting the delivery status - field, then a SingleTargetNotificationResponse contains the target's response message as an array of bytes.
